gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 102, Spurs 94
gameRecap.excerpt: Minnesota defeated San Antonio, 102-94. Mike Conley led Minnesota with 18 points, four rebounds, and four assists as Anthony Edwards (17 points, seven rebounds, six assists) and Rudy Gobert (16 points, 20 rebounds) totaled 33 points. Devin Vassell led San Antonio with 22 points as Keldon Johnson (21 points, 10 rebounds) and Victor Wembanyama (12 points, 10 rebounds, one block, one steal) totaled 33 points.
